\v 23 E o <a name="01100102300004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">fizeram</a> <a name="01100102300004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">saber</a> ao <a name="01100102300010" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, <a name="01100102300014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: Aí está o <a name="01100102300022" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a> <a name="01100102300018" ll="SDBH:נָתָן:000001">Natã</a>. <a name="01100102300026">Apresentou</a>-se ele <a name="01100102300030">ao</a> <a name="01100102300034" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, <a name="01100102300038" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">prostrou</a>-<a name="01100102300038" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">se</a> com o <a name="01100102300048" ll="SDBH:אַף:000002">rosto</a> <a name="01100102300050" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">em</a> <a name="01100102300050" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> perante <a name="01100102300044" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">ele</a> 
