\v 34 <a name="01100103400010" ll="SDBH:צָדֹוק:000000">Zadoque</a>, o <a name="01100103400014" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdote</a>, com <a name="01100103400018" ll="SDBH:נָתָן:000001">Natã</a>, o <a name="01100103400022" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a>, ali o <a name="01100103400004" ll="SDBH:משׁח:000001" il="Anoint">ungirão</a> <a name="01100103400026" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> sobre <a name="01100103400030" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>; então, <a name="01100103400034" ll="SDBH:תקע:000006">tocareis</a> a <a name="01100103400040" ll="SDBH:שֹׁופָר:000000" il="BK00179;HK00188;LB00186;NBGmk20140407c;Realia:7.3.1c">trombeta</a> e <a name="01100103400044" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">direis</a>: <a name="01100103400046" ll="SDBH:חיה:000000">Viva</a> o <a name="01100103400050" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100103400052" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>! 
\v 35 <a name="01100103500004" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">Subireis</a> <a name="01100103500006" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001002">após</a> <a name="01100103500006" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001002">ele</a>, e <a name="01100103500010">virá</a> e <a name="01100103500014">se</a> <a name="01100103500014">assentará</a> no <a name="01100103500018" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">meu</a> <a name="01100103500018" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">trono</a>, pois é ele quem <a name="01100103500024" ll="SDBH:מלך:000000">reinará</a> em meu lugar; porque <a name="01100103500032" ll="SDBH:צוה:000001">ordenei</a> seja ele <a name="01100103500038" ll="SDBH:נָגִיד:000000">príncipe</a> sobre <a name="01100103500042" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a> e sobre <a name="01100103500048" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>. 
