\v 37 Como o <a name="01100103700008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> foi com o <a name="01100103700016" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>, <a name="01100103700012" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="01100103700012" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>, assim seja com <a name="01100103700026" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> e <a name="01100103700030" ll="SDBH:גדל:000008">faça</a> <a name="01100103700030" ll="SDBH:גדל:000008">que</a> o <a name="01100103700034" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">trono</a> <a name="01100103700034" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">deste</a> <a name="01100103700030" ll="SDBH:גדל:000008">seja</a> <a name="01100103700030" ll="SDBH:גדל:000008">maior</a> do que o <a name="01100103700038" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">trono</a> do <a name="01100103700044" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100103700046" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01100103700040" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">meu</a> <a name="01100103700040" ll="SDBH:אָדֹון:000000">senhor</a>.
    
\v 38 Então, <a name="01100103800004" ll="SDBH:ירד:000001">desceu</a> <a name="01100103800006" ll="SDBH:צָדֹוק:000000">Zadoque</a>, o <a name="01100103800010" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdote</a>, e <a name="01100103800014" ll="SDBH:נָתָן:000001">Natã</a>, o <a name="01100103800018" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a>, e <a name="01100103800022" ll="SDBH:בְּנָיָהוּ:000000">Benaia</a>, <a name="01100103800024" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> <a name="01100103800026" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָדָע:000000">de</a> <a name="01100103800026" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָדָע:000000">Joiada</a>, e a <a name="01100103800032;01100103800038" ll="SDBH:כְּרֵתִי:000001;SDBH:פְּלֵתִי:000000">guarda</a> <a name="01100103800032;01100103800038" ll="SDBH:כְּרֵתִי:000001;SDBH:פְּלֵתִי:000000">real</a>, <a name="01100103800042" ll="SDBH:רכב:000001">fizeram</a> <a name="01100103800042" ll="SDBH:רכב:000001">montar</a> <a name="01100103800046" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> a <a name="01100103800050" ll="SDBH:פִּרְדָּה:000000">mula</a> que era do <a name="01100103800054" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100103800056" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a> e o <a name="01100103800060" ll="SDBH:הלך:000003">levaram</a> a <a name="01100103800066" ll="SDBH:גִּיחֹון:000001" il="adr1305123466">Giom</a>. 
\v 39 <a name="01100103900006" ll="SDBH:צָדֹוק:000000">Zadoque</a>, o <a name="01100103900010" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdote</a>, <a name="01100103900004" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomou</a> do <a name="01100103900024" ll="SDBH:אֹהֶל:000000" il="HK00223;NBGbs20090406-1_27;NBGbs20090428_2;NBGbs20120713-532">tabernáculo</a> o <a name="01100103900014" ll="SDBH:קֶרֶן:000001" il="BK00179;NBGmk20140407c;Realia:7.3.1c;adr1305240961">chifre</a> do <a name="01100103900018" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶן:000000" il="Italian_olive_oil_2007;NBGbs20100214-0211;il_oil_press_d01">azeite</a> e <a name="01100103900028" ll="SDBH:משׁח:000001" il="Anoint">ungiu</a> a <a name="01100103900032" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>; <a name="01100103900036" ll="SDBH:תקע:000006">tocaram</a> a <a name="01100103900042" ll="SDBH:שֹׁופָר:000000" il="BK00179;HK00188;LB00186;NBGmk20140407c;Realia:7.3.1c">trombeta</a>, e todo o <a name="01100103900052" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="01100103900046" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">exclamou</a>: <a name="01100103900054" ll="SDBH:חיה:000000">Viva</a> o <a name="01100103900058" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100103900060" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>! 
\v 40 <a name="01100104000012" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000">Após</a> <a name="01100104000012" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000">ele</a>, <a name="01100104000004" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">subiu</a> todo o <a name="01100104000010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a>, <a name="01100104000020" ll="SDBH:חלל:003000" il="Kerffluit_van_bamboe;LB00189;NBGmk20130414">tocando</a> <a name="01100104000024" ll="SDBH:חָלִיל:000000" il="Kerffluit_van_bamboe;LB00189;NBGmk20130414">gaitas</a> e <a name="01100104000028" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">alegrando</a>-<a name="01100104000028" ll="SDBH:שׂמח:000000">se</a> com <a name="01100104000032" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000003">grande</a> <a name="01100104000030" ll="SDBH:שִׂמְחָה:000000">alegria</a>, de maneira que, com o <a name="01100104000044">seu</a> <a name="01100104000044">clamor</a>, parecia <a name="01100104000036" ll="SDBH:בקע:000000">fender</a>-<a name="01100104000036" ll="SDBH:בקע:000000">se</a> a <a name="01100104000040" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>.
    
\v 41 <a name="01100104100006" ll="SDBH:אֲדֹנִיָּהוּ:000000">Adonias</a> e todos os <a name="01100104100014" ll="SDBH:קרא:000003">convidados</a> que com ele estavam o <a name="01100104100004">ouviram</a>, quando <a name="01100104100024" ll="SDBH:כלה:000001">acabavam</a> de <a name="01100104100028" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">comer</a>; também <a name="01100104100034" ll="SDBH:יֹואָב:000000">Joabe</a> <a name="01100104100032">ouviu</a> o <a name="01100104100038">sonido</a> das <a name="01100104100042" ll="SDBH:שֹׁופָר:000000" il="BK00179;HK00188;LB00186;NBGmk20140407c;Realia:7.3.1c">trombetas</a> e <a name="01100104100046" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Que significa esse <a name="01100104100050">ruído</a> de <a name="01100104100054" ll="SDBH:קִרְיָה:000000">cidade</a> <a name="01100104100056" ll="SDBH:המה:000000">alvoroçada</a>? 
