\v 41 <a name="01100204100004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">Foi</a> <a name="01100204100008" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> <a name="01100204100004" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">avisado</a> de que <a name="01100204100014" ll="SDBH:שִׁמְעִי:000001">Simei</a> de <a name="01100204100018" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a> <a name="01100204100012" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">fora</a> a <a name="01100204100020" ll="SDBH:גַּת:001000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00002;Satellite Bible Atlas00003;Satellite Bible Atlas00013;adr08072471511">Gate</a> e já <a name="01100204100024" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">havia</a> <a name="01100204100024" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">voltado</a>. 
\v 42 Então, <a name="01100204200004" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000003">mandou</a> o <a name="01100204200008" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100204200012" ll="SDBH:קרא:000003">chamar</a> a <a name="01100204200016" ll="SDBH:שִׁמְעִי:000001">Simei</a> e lhe <a name="01100204200020" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Não <a name="01100204200028" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000003" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">te</a> <a name="01100204200028" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000003" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">fiz</a> <a name="01100204200028" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000003" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">eu</a> <a name="01100204200028" ll="SDBH:שׁבע:000003" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">jurar</a> pelo <a name="01100204200032" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> e não te <a name="01100204200036" ll="SDBH:עוד:000002">protestei</a>, <a name="01100204200042" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: No <a name="01100204200046" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000003">dia</a> em <a name="01100204200048" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">que</a> <a name="01100204200048" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saíres</a> para <a name="01100204200054;01100204200056;01100204200058" ll="SDBH:אָן:000000">uma</a> <a name="01100204200054;01100204200056;01100204200058" ll="SDBH:אָן:000000">ou</a> <a name="01100204200054;01100204200056;01100204200058" ll="SDBH:אָן:000000">outra</a> <a name="01100204200054;01100204200056;01100204200058" ll="SDBH:אָן:000000">parte</a>, fica sabendo que serás morto? E tu me <a name="01100204200072" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disseste</a>: <a name="01100204200076" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">Boa</a> é essa <a name="01100204200080" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="01100204200082">que</a> <a name="01100204200082">ouvi</a>. 
\v 43 Por que, pois, não <a name="01100204300008" ll="SDBH:שׁמר:000003">guardaste</a> o <a name="01100204300012" ll="SDBH:שְׁבוּעָה:000000" il="Oath_Jacob_Esau">juramento</a> do <a name="01100204300014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, nem a <a name="01100204300022" ll="SDBH:מִצְוָה:000000">ordem</a> que te <a name="01100204300026" ll="SDBH:צוה:000001">dei</a>? 
\v 44 <a name="01100204400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a> mais o <a name="01100204400008" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> a <a name="01100204400012" ll="SDBH:שִׁמְעִי:000001">Simei</a>: Bem <a name="01100204400016">sabes</a> toda a <a name="01100204400024" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000002">maldade</a> que o <a name="01100204400030" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">teu</a> <a name="01100204400030" ll="SDBH:לֵבָב:000001">coração</a> <a name="01100204400028">reconhece</a> que <a name="01100204400034">fizeste</a> a <a name="01100204400038" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01100204400040" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">meu</a> <a name="01100204400040" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>; pelo que o <a name="01100204400046" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> te <a name="01100204400044" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000032">fez</a> <a name="01100204400044" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000032">recair</a> sobre <a name="01100204400054" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">a</a> <a name="01100204400054" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000000">cabeça</a> a <a name="01100204400050" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000000">tua</a> <a name="01100204400050" ll="SDBH:רָעָה:000000">maldade</a>. 
\v 45 Mas o <a name="01100204500006" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100204500008" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> será <a name="01100204500010" ll="SDBH:ברך:001001">abençoado</a>, e o <a name="01100204500014" ll="SDBH:כִּסֵּא:000002" il="Darius_In_Parse;Roman_throne;Throne_Greek;Throne_Toutankamon;mb120901102">trono</a> de <a name="01100204500016" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01100204500020" ll="SDBH:כון:000015">mantido</a> <a name="01100204500024">perante</a> o <a name="01100204500026" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="01100204500028" ll="SDBH:עַד:000001">para</a> <a name="01100204500030" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">sempre</a>. 
\v 46 O <a name="01100204600008" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01100204600004" ll="SDBH:צוה:000001">deu</a> <a name="01100204600004" ll="SDBH:צוה:000001">ordem</a> a <a name="01100204600012" ll="SDBH:בְּנָיָהוּ:000000">Benaia</a>, <a name="01100204600014" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> <a name="01100204600016" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָדָע:000000">de</a> <a name="01100204600016" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָדָע:000000">Joiada</a>, o qual <a name="01100204600020" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saiu</a> e <a name="01100204600024" ll="SDBH:פגע:000002">arremeteu</a> contra ele, de sorte que <a name="01100204600030" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">morreu</a>; assim <a name="01100204600038" ll="SDBH:כון:000015">se</a> <a name="01100204600038" ll="SDBH:כון:000015">firmou</a> o <a name="01100204600036" ll="SDBH:מַמְלָכָה:000000">reino</a> sob o <a name="01100204600042">domínio</a> <a name="01100204600044" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">de</a> <a name="01100204600044" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>.
\c 3
\v 1 <a name="01100300100006" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> <a name="01100300100004" ll="SDBH:חתן:000000" il="ef0078">aparentou</a>-<a name="01100300100004" ll="SDBH:חתן:000000" il="ef0078">se</a> com <a name="01100300100010" ll="SDBH:פַּרְעֹה:000000" il="tb010705951">Faraó</a>, <a name="01100300100012" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> do <a name="01100300100014" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">Egito</a>, pois <a name="01100300100018" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomou</a> por mulher a <a name="01100300100022" ll="SDBH:בַּת:000000">filha</a> <a name="01100300100024" ll="SDBH:פַּרְעֹה:000000" il="tb010705951">de</a> <a name="01100300100024" ll="SDBH:פַּרְעֹה:000000" il="tb010705951">Faraó</a> e <a name="01100300100028">a</a> <a name="01100300100028">trouxe</a> à <a name="01100300100032" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000001">Cidade</a> de <a name="01100300100034" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, até que <a name="01100300100038" ll="SDBH:כלה:000001">acabasse</a> de <a name="01100300100042" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">edificar</a> a <a name="01100300100046" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">sua</a> <a name="01100300100046" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">casa</a>, e a Casa do <a name="01100300100054" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, e a <a name="01100300100060" ll="SDBH:חֹומָה:000000">muralha</a> <a name="01100300100064" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">à</a> <a name="01100300100064" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">roda</a> <a name="01100300100064" ll="SDBH:סָבִיב:000000">de</a> <a name="01100300100062" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a>. 
\v 2 Entretanto, o <a name="01100300200006" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="01100300200008" ll="SDBH:זבח:000001">oferecia</a> <a name="01100300200008" ll="SDBH:זבח:000001">sacrifícios</a> sobre os <a name="01100300200014" ll="SDBH:בָּמָה:000002" il="Flora:1.18.1a;adr0807089001;ws040616035">altos</a>, porque até àqueles <a name="01100300200034" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000002">dias</a> ainda não <a name="01100300200020" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">se</a> <a name="01100300200020" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">tinha</a> <a name="01100300200020" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">edificado</a> <a name="01100300200022" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">casa</a> ao <a name="01100300200026" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000003">nome</a> do <a name="01100300200028" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>.
    
\v 3 <a name="01100300300006" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> <a name="01100300300004" ll="SDBH:אהב:000000">amava</a> ao <a name="01100300300010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="01100300300014" ll="SDBH:הלך:000004">andando</a> nos <a name="01100300300018" ll="SDBH:חֻקָּה:000001">preceitos</a> de <a name="01100300300020" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01100300300022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">seu</a> <a name="01100300300022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>; porém <a name="01100300300034" ll="SDBH:זבח:000001">sacrificava</a> ainda nos <a name="01100300300030" ll="SDBH:בָּמָה:000002" il="Flora:1.18.1a;adr0807089001;ws040616035">altos</a> e <a name="01100300300038" ll="SDBH:קטר:000000">queimava</a> <a name="01100300300038" ll="SDBH:קטר:000000">incenso</a>. 
