\v 7 Eu, contudo, não <a name="01101000700006" ll="SDBH:אמן:000004">cria</a> naquelas <a name="01101000700012" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a>, até que <a name="01101000700018">vim</a> e <a name="01101000700022" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vi</a> com os <a name="01101000700024" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">meus</a> próprios <a name="01101000700024" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a>. Eis que não me <a name="01101000700032" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">contaram</a> a <a name="01101000700038" ll="SDBH:חֲצִי:000002">metade</a>: <a name="01101000700040">sobrepujas</a> em <a name="01101000700042" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">sabedoria</a> e <a name="01101000700046" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000002">prosperidade</a> a <a name="01101000700052" ll="SDBH:שְׁמוּעָה:000000">fama</a> que <a name="01101000700056">ouvi</a>. 
\v 8 <a name="01101000800002" ll="SDBH:אַשְׁרֵי:000000">Felizes</a> os teus homens, <a name="01101000800006" ll="SDBH:אַשְׁרֵי:000000">felizes</a> estes <a name="01101000800008" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">teus</a> <a name="01101000800008" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servos</a>, que <a name="01101000800014">estão</a> <a name="01101000800020" ll="SDBH:תָּמִיד:000000">sempre</a> <a name="01101000800018">diante</a> <a name="01101000800018">de</a> <a name="01101000800018">ti</a> e que <a name="01101000800024">ouvem</a> a <a name="01101000800028" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">tua</a> <a name="01101000800028" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">sabedoria</a>! 
