\v 13 O <a name="01101001300006" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01101001300008" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> <a name="01101001300010">deu</a> à <a name="01101001300014" ll="SDBH:מַלְכָּה:000000">rainha</a> de <a name="01101001300016" ll="SDBH:שְׁבָא:000003">Sabá</a> tudo quanto <a name="01101001300022" ll="SDBH:חֵפֶץ:000002">ela</a> <a name="01101001300022" ll="SDBH:חֵפֶץ:000002">desejou</a> e <a name="01101001300026" ll="SDBH:שׁאל:000000">pediu</a>, afora tudo o que lhe <a name="01101001300036">deu</a> por sua <a name="01101001300042">generosidade</a> <a name="01101001300046" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">real</a>. Assim, <a name="01101001300052" ll="SDBH:פנה:000000">voltou</a> e <a name="01101001300056" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">se</a> <a name="01101001300056" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">foi</a> para a <a name="01101001300060" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">sua</a> <a name="01101001300060" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>, com os <a name="01101001300066" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">seus</a> <a name="01101001300066" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servos</a>.
    
