\v 26 <a name="01101102600004" ll="SDBH:יָרָבְעָם:000000">Jeroboão</a>, <a name="01101102600006" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> <a name="01101102600008" ll="SDBH:נְבָט:000000">de</a> <a name="01101102600008" ll="SDBH:נְבָט:000000">Nebate</a>, <a name="01101102600010" ll="SDBH:אֶפְרָתִי:001000">efraimita</a> de <a name="01101102600016" ll="SDBH:צְרֵדָה:000000">Zereda</a>, <a name="01101102600030" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servo</a> de <a name="01101102600034" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>, e <a name="01101102600022" ll="SDBH:אֵם:000000" il="Motherhood1912">cuja</a> <a name="01101102600022" ll="SDBH:אֵם:000000" il="Motherhood1912">mãe</a> era <a name="01101102600026" ll="SDBH:אִשָּׁה:000000">mulher</a> <a name="01101102600028" ll="SDBH:אַלְמָנָה:000000">viúva</a>, por <a name="01101102600020" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000000">nome</a> <a name="01101102600024" ll="SDBH:צְרוּעָה:000000">Zerua</a>, <a name="01101102600038" ll="SDBH:רום:000035">levantou</a> a <a name="01101102600040">mão</a> contra o <a name="01101102600046" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>. 
\v 27 Esta foi a <a name="01101102700008" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">causa</a> por que <a name="01101102700012" ll="SDBH:רום:000035">levantou</a> a <a name="01101102700014">mão</a> contra o <a name="01101102700020" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a>: <a name="01101102700022" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> estava <a name="01101102700024" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">edificando</a> a <a name="01101102700030" ll="SDBH:מִלֹּוא:000000">Milo</a> e <a name="01101102700032" ll="SDBH:סגר:000002">terraplenando</a> <a name="01101102700036" ll="SDBH:פֶּרֶץ:000000">depressões</a> da <a name="01101102700038" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000001">Cidade</a> de <a name="01101102700040" ll="SDBH:דָּוִד:000000">Davi</a>, <a name="01101102700042" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">seu</a> <a name="01101102700042" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>. 
