\v 29 Sucedeu, nesse <a name="01101102900010" ll="SDBH:עֵת:000000">tempo</a>, que, <a name="01101102900020" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">saindo</a> <a name="01101102900018" ll="SDBH:יָרָבְעָם:000000">Jeroboão</a> de <a name="01101102900024" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a>, o <a name="01101102900028" ll="SDBH:מצא:000012">encontrou</a> o <a name="01101102900040" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a> <a name="01101102900032" ll="SDBH:אֲחִיָּה:000002">Aías</a>, o <a name="01101102900036" ll="SDBH:שִׁילֹנִי:000000">silonita</a>, no <a name="01101102900046" ll="SDBH:דֶּרֶךְ:000003">caminho</a>; este <a name="01101102900052" ll="SDBH:כסה:000008">se</a> <a name="01101102900052" ll="SDBH:כסה:000008">tinha</a> <a name="01101102900052" ll="SDBH:כסה:000008">vestido</a> de uma <a name="01101102900056" ll="SDBH:שַׂלְמָה:000000">capa</a> <a name="01101102900058" ll="SDBH:חָדָשׁ:000000">nova</a>, e estavam sós <a name="01101102900062" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">os</a> <a name="01101102900062" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> no <a name="01101102900072" ll="SDBH:שָׂדֶה:000000">campo</a>. 
