\v 40 Pelo que <a name="01101104000006" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a> <a name="01101104000004" ll="SDBH:בקשׁ:000005">procurou</a> <a name="01101104000010" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">matar</a> a <a name="01101104000014" ll="SDBH:יָרָבְעָם:000000">Jeroboão</a>; <a name="01101104000020" ll="SDBH:יָרָבְעָם:000000">este</a>, porém, <a name="01101104000018">se</a> <a name="01101104000018">dispôs</a> e <a name="01101104000024" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">fugiu</a> para o <a name="01101104000026" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">Egito</a>, a ter com <a name="01101104000030" ll="SDBH:שִׁישַׁק:000000">Sisaque</a>, <a name="01101104000032" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01101104000034" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">do</a> <a name="01101104000034" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">Egito</a>; e <a name="01101104000042" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">ali</a> permaneceu até à <a name="01101104000046" ll="SDBH:מָוֶת:000000">morte</a> de <a name="01101104000048" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>.
    
\v 41 Quanto aos <a name="01101104100004" ll="SDBH:יֶתֶר:000003">mais</a> <a name="01101104100006" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">atos</a> de <a name="01101104100008" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>, a tudo quanto <a name="01101104100016">fez</a>, e à <a name="01101104100020" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">sua</a> <a name="01101104100020" ll="SDBH:חָכְמָה:000000">sabedoria</a>, porventura, não estão <a name="01101104100028" ll="SDBH:כתב:000000" il="Scribe at work;WritingScroll-ReedPen-01-065d;tb032014452">escritos</a> no <a name="01101104100032" ll="SDBH:סֵפֶר:000003">Livro</a> da <a name="01101104100034" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">História</a> de <a name="01101104100036" ll="SDBH:שְׁלֹמֹה:000000">Salomão</a>? 
