\v 19 Ele lhe <a name="01101701900004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: <a name="01101701900008">Dá</a>-me o <a name="01101701900014" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">teu</a> <a name="01101701900014" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a>; <a name="01101701900018" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomou</a>-<a name="01101701900018" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">o</a> dos <a name="01101701900022" ll="SDBH:חֵיק:000000">braços</a> <a name="01101701900022" ll="SDBH:חֵיק:000000">dela</a>, e <a name="01101701900026" ll="SDBH:עלה:000005">o</a> <a name="01101701900026" ll="SDBH:עלה:000005">levou</a> para cima, ao <a name="01101701900032" ll="SDBH:עֲלִיָּה:000000">quarto</a>, onde ele mesmo <a name="01101701900038">se</a> <a name="01101701900038">hospedava</a>, e <a name="01101701900044" ll="SDBH:שׁכב:000001">o</a> <a name="01101701900044" ll="SDBH:שׁכב:000001">deitou</a> em <a name="01101701900048" ll="SDBH:מִטָּה:000000" il="Realia:5.5b;Realia:5.5c;tb052916236">sua</a> <a name="01101701900048" ll="SDBH:מִטָּה:000000" il="Realia:5.5b;Realia:5.5c;tb052916236">cama</a>; 
