\v 12 Poderá ser que, <a name="01101801200008" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">apartando</a>-<a name="01101801200008" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">me</a> eu de ti, o <a name="01101801200016" ll="SDBH:רוּחַ:000000">Espírito</a> do <a name="01101801200018" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="01101801200020" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000019">te</a> <a name="01101801200020" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000019">leve</a> não <a name="01101801200028">sei</a> para onde, e, <a name="01101801200032">vindo</a> eu a <a name="01101801200036" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">dar</a> <a name="01101801200036" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">as</a> <a name="01101801200036" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">novas</a> a <a name="01101801200040" ll="SDBH:אַחְאָב:000000">Acabe</a>, e não <a name="01101801200046" ll="SDBH:מצא:000000">te</a> <a name="01101801200046" ll="SDBH:מצא:000000">achando</a> <a name="01101801200046" ll="SDBH:מצא:000000">ele</a>, <a name="01101801200050" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">me</a> <a name="01101801200050" ll="SDBH:הרג:000000">matará</a>; eu, contudo, <a name="01101801200054" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">teu</a> <a name="01101801200054" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servo</a>, <a name="01101801200056" ll="SDBH:ירא:000000">temo</a> ao <a name="01101801200060" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> desde a <a name="01101801200064" ll="SDBH:נְעוּרִים:000000">minha</a> <a name="01101801200064" ll="SDBH:נְעוּרִים:000000">mocidade</a>. 
