\v 34 e <a name="01101803400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: <a name="01101803400006" ll="SDBH:מלא:000002">Enchei</a> de <a name="01101803400012" ll="SDBH:מַיִם:000000" il="Water_drop_001">água</a> <a name="01101803400008" ll="SDBH:אַרְבַּע:000000">quatro</a> <a name="01101803400010" ll="SDBH:כַּד:000000" il="NBGmk20140119d;NBGmk20140119g;Realia:5.18.1.2;adr1305228181">cântaros</a> e <a name="01101803400016" ll="SDBH:יצק:000002">derramai</a>-a sobre o <a name="01101803400022" ll="SDBH:עֹלָה:000000" il="HK00251;HK00256;LB00253;LB00254;LB00255;NBGlo20140504a;NBGlo20140504b;NBGlo20140504c;Realia:4.2.3">holocausto</a> e sobre a <a name="01101803400030" ll="SDBH:עֵץ:000001">lenha</a>. <a name="01101803400034" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Disse</a> ainda: <a name="01101803400036" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">Fazei</a>-<a name="01101803400036" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">o</a> <a name="01101803400036" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">segunda</a> <a name="01101803400036" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">vez</a>; e o <a name="01101803400040" ll="SDBH:שׁנה:000007">fizeram</a>. Disse mais: <a name="01101803400046" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">Fazei</a>-<a name="01101803400046" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">o</a> <a name="01101803400046" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">terceira</a> <a name="01101803400046" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">vez</a>; e o <a name="01101803400050" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">fizeram</a> <a name="01101803400050" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">terceira</a> <a name="01101803400050" ll="SDBH:שׁלשׁ:000000">vez</a>. 
