\v 42 <a name="01101804200004" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">Subiu</a> <a name="01101804200006" ll="SDBH:אַחְאָב:000000">Acabe</a> a <a name="01101804200010" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">comer</a> e a <a name="01101804200016" ll="SDBH:שׁתה:000000">beber</a>; <a name="01101804200020" ll="SDBH:אֵלִיָּהוּ:000000">Elias</a>, porém, <a name="01101804200022" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">subiu</a> ao <a name="01101804200026" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000011">cimo</a> do <a name="01101804200030" ll="SDBH:כַּרְמֶל:001001" il="Bolen00052;Satellite Bible Atlas00011;tb050900101;tb052500101">Carmelo</a>, e, <a name="01101804200034" ll="SDBH:גהר:000000">encurvado</a> para a <a name="01101804200036" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>, <a name="01101804200040" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000001">meteu</a> o <a name="01101804200042" ll="SDBH:פָּנֶה:000000">rosto</a> entre <a name="01101804200048" ll="SDBH:בֶּרֶךְ:000000">os</a> <a name="01101804200048" ll="SDBH:בֶּרֶךְ:000000">joelhos</a>, 
