\v 44 À <a name="01101804400010" ll="SDBH:שְׁבִיעִי:000000">sétima</a> <a name="01101804400010" ll="SDBH:שְׁבִיעִי:000000">vez</a> <a name="01101804400014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Eis que <a name="01101804400028" ll="SDBH:עלה:000000">se</a> <a name="01101804400028" ll="SDBH:עלה:000000">levanta</a> do <a name="01101804400032" ll="SDBH:יָם:000001" il="Rough_seas">mar</a> uma <a name="01101804400018" ll="SDBH:עָב:000000" il="Altocumulus_cloud;White_cloud_111">nuvem</a> <a name="01101804400020" ll="SDBH:קָטָן:000000">pequena</a> como a palma da <a name="01101804400024" ll="SDBH:כַּף:000000">mão</a> do <a name="01101804400026">homem</a>. Então, <a name="01101804400036" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> ele: <a name="01101804400038" ll="SDBH:עלה:000004">Sobe</a> e <a name="01101804400040" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dize</a> a <a name="01101804400044" ll="SDBH:אַחְאָב:000000">Acabe</a>: <a name="01101804400046" ll="SDBH:אסר:000002">Aparelha</a> o teu carro e <a name="01101804400050" ll="SDBH:ירד:000001">desce</a>, para que a <a name="01101804400060" ll="SDBH:גֶּשֶׁם:000000" il="Rain;Rain2">chuva</a> não <a name="01101804400056" ll="SDBH:עצר:000001">te</a> <a name="01101804400056" ll="SDBH:עצר:000001">detenha</a>. 
