\v 12 <a name="01102001200008">Tendo</a> Ben-Hadade <a name="01102001200008">ouvido</a> esta <a name="01102001200014" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">resposta</a>, quando <a name="01102001200024" ll="SDBH:שׁתה:000000">bebiam</a> ele e os <a name="01102001200032" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">reis</a> nas <a name="01102001200038" ll="SDBH:סֻכָּה:000000">tendas</a>, <a name="01102001200042" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> aos <a name="01102001200046" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">seus</a> <a name="01102001200046" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000" il="Bolen00049">servos</a>: <a name="01102001200048" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">Ponde</a>-<a name="01102001200048" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">vos</a> <a name="01102001200048" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">de</a> <a name="01102001200048" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">prontidão</a>. E eles <a name="01102001200052" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">se</a> <a name="01102001200052" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">puseram</a> <a name="01102001200052" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">de</a> <a name="01102001200052" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000000">prontidão</a> contra a <a name="01102001200058" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a>.
    
\v 13 Eis que <a name="01102001300008" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">um</a> <a name="01102001300006" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a> <a name="01102001300010" ll="SDBH:נגשׁ:000002">se</a> <a name="01102001300010" ll="SDBH:נגשׁ:000002">chegou</a> a <a name="01102001300014" ll="SDBH:אַחְאָב:000000">Acabe</a>, <a name="01102001300016" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="01102001300018" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">de</a> <a name="01102001300018" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, e lhe <a name="01102001300022" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Assim <a name="01102001300026" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="01102001300028" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>: <a name="01102001300032" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">Viste</a> toda esta <a name="01102001300044" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000000">grande</a> <a name="01102001300040" ll="SDBH:הָמֹון:000002">multidão</a>? Pois, <a name="01102001300060" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000005">hoje</a>, <a name="01102001300052">a</a> <a name="01102001300052">entregarei</a> nas <a name="01102001300056">tuas</a> <a name="01102001300056">mãos</a>, e <a name="01102001300064">saberás</a> que eu sou o <a name="01102001300070" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>. 
\v 14 <a name="01102001400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Perguntou</a> <a name="01102001400006" ll="SDBH:אַחְאָב:000000">Acabe</a>: Por quem? Ele <a name="01102001400014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">respondeu</a>: Assim <a name="01102001400018" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="01102001400020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>: Pelos <a name="01102001400024" ll="SDBH:נַעַר:000000">moços</a> <a name="01102001400026" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">dos</a> <a name="01102001400026" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">chefes</a> das <a name="01102001400030" ll="SDBH:מְדִינָה:000000">províncias</a>. E <a name="01102001400034" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>: Quem <a name="01102001400038" ll="SDBH:אסר:000009">começará</a> a <a name="01102001400042" ll="SDBH:מִלְחָמָה:000000">peleja</a>? Tu! — <a name="01102001400046" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">respondeu</a> <a name="01102001400046" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">ele</a>. 
\v 15 Então, <a name="01102001500004" ll="SDBH:פקד:000001">contou</a> os <a name="01102001500008" ll="SDBH:נַעַר:000000">moços</a> <a name="01102001500010" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">dos</a> <a name="01102001500010" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">chefes</a> das <a name="01102001500014" ll="SDBH:מְדִינָה:000000">províncias</a>, e eram <a name="01102001500020" ll="SDBH:מֵאָה:000000">duzentos</a> e <a name="01102001500026" ll="SDBH:שָׁלֹשׁ:000001">trinta</a> e <a name="01102001500022" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a>; <a name="01102001500030" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001002">depois</a>, <a name="01102001500032" ll="SDBH:פקד:000001">contou</a> todo o <a name="01102001500040" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a>, todos os <a name="01102001500044" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filhos</a> de <a name="01102001500046" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, <a name="01102001500048" ll="SDBH:שֶׁבַע:000000">sete</a> <a name="01102001500050" ll="SDBH:אֶלֶף:001000">mil</a>.
    
\v 16 <a name="01102001600004" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">Saíram</a> ao <a name="01102001600010" ll="SDBH:צָהֳרַיִם:000000" il="Sun">meio</a>-<a name="01102001600010" ll="SDBH:צָהֳרַיִם:000000" il="Sun">dia</a>. <a name="01102001600014" ll="SDBH:בֶּן־הֲדַד:000000">Ben</a>-<a name="01102001600014" ll="SDBH:בֶּן־הֲדַד:000000">Hadade</a>, porém, estava <a name="01102001600016" ll="SDBH:שׁתה:000000">bebendo</a> e <a name="01102001600018" ll="SDBH:שִׁכֹּור:000000">embriagando</a>-<a name="01102001600018" ll="SDBH:שִׁכֹּור:000000">se</a> nas <a name="01102001600024" ll="SDBH:סֻכָּה:000000">tendas</a>, ele e os <a name="01102001600032" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">reis</a>, os <a name="01102001600034" ll="SDBH:שָׁלֹשׁ:000001">trinta</a> e <a name="01102001600038" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> <a name="01102001600040" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">reis</a> que o <a name="01102001600042" ll="SDBH:עזר:000001">ajudavam</a>. 
\v 17 <a name="01102001700004" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">Saíram</a> <a name="01102001700018" ll="SDBH:רִאשֹׁון:000000">primeiro</a> os <a name="01102001700006" ll="SDBH:נַעַר:000000">moços</a> <a name="01102001700008" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">dos</a> <a name="01102001700008" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">chefes</a> das <a name="01102001700012" ll="SDBH:מְדִינָה:000000">províncias</a>; <a name="01102001700024" ll="SDBH:בֶּן־הֲדַד:000000" tl="HOTTP1360">Ben</a>-<a name="01102001700024" ll="SDBH:בֶּן־הֲדַד:000000" tl="HOTTP1360">Hadade</a> <a name="01102001700022" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000003" tl="HOTTP1360">mandou</a> observadores que lhe <a name="01102001700028" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">deram</a> <a name="01102001700028" ll="SDBH:נגד:000000">avisos</a>, <a name="01102001700034" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: <a name="01102001700038" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">Saíram</a> de <a name="01102001700042" ll="SDBH:שֹׁמְרֹון:000000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00014;tb070507860">Samaria</a> uns homens. 
