\v 19 <a name="01102001900006" ll="SDBH:יצא:000000">Saíram</a>, pois, da <a name="01102001900012" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> os <a name="01102001900014" ll="SDBH:נַעַר:000000">moços</a> <a name="01102001900016" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">dos</a> <a name="01102001900016" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">chefes</a> das <a name="01102001900020" ll="SDBH:מְדִינָה:000000">províncias</a> e o <a name="01102001900026" ll="SDBH:חַיִל:000002" il="HK00197;LB00198;NBGmk20131008a;adr1603195037">exército</a> que <a name="01102001900030" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000">os</a> <a name="01102001900030" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001000">seguia</a>. 
