\v 34 Ben-Hadade <a name="01102003400004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a>-lhe: As <a name="01102003400010" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidades</a> que <a name="01102003400016" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">meu</a> <a name="01102003400016" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a> <a name="01102003400014" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">tomou</a> a <a name="01102003400022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">teu</a> <a name="01102003400022" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a>, <a name="01102003400024" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">eu</a> tas <a name="01102003400024" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">restituirei</a>; <a name="01102003400030" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000001">monta</a> os teus <a name="01102003400028" ll="SDBH:חוּץ:000005" il="HK00169;Realia:3.13.2;tb052001215">bazares</a> em <a name="01102003400036" ll="SDBH:דַּמֶּשֶׂק:000000" il="HK00375;mat01135;mat07576;tb110406671">Damasco</a>, como <a name="01102003400044" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">meu</a> <a name="01102003400044" ll="SDBH:אָב:000000">pai</a> o <a name="01102003400042" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000001">fez</a> em <a name="01102003400048" ll="SDBH:שֹׁמְרֹון:000000" il="Satellite Bible Atlas00014;tb070507860">Samaria</a>. E eu, disse Acabe, com esta <a name="01102003400058" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000" il="Treaty_of_Kadesh">aliança</a>, <a name="01102003400060" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">te</a> <a name="01102003400060" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">deixarei</a> <a name="01102003400060" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">livre</a>. <a name="01102003400064" ll="SDBH:כרת:000001">Fez</a> com ele <a name="01102003400068" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000" il="Treaty_of_Kadesh">aliança</a> e <a name="01102003400072" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">o</a> <a name="01102003400072" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000009">despediu</a>.
    
\v 35 Então, <a name="01102003500006" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">um</a> dos <a name="01102003500004;01102003500010" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000003">discípulos</a> dos <a name="01102003500014" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profetas</a> <a name="01102003500016" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> ao <a name="01102003500020" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">seu</a> <a name="01102003500020" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">companheiro</a> por <a name="01102003500024" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">ordem</a> do <a name="01102003500026" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>: <a name="01102003500028">Esmurra</a>-<a name="01102003500028">me</a>; mas o <a name="01102003500038">homem</a> <a name="01102003500034" ll="SDBH:מאן:000000">recusou</a> <a name="01102003500042">fazê</a>-<a name="01102003500042">lo</a>. 
